# game/OpeningScript.rpy:3
translate korean Opening_ifDead_1978d1a2:

    # "It seemed they had a restless dream last night, perhaps due to the commotion."
    "지난 밤의 소동 때문인지 소란스러운 꿈을 꾼 것 같습니다."

# game/OpeningScript.rpy:4
translate korean Opening_ifDead_8c3d0abe:

    # "The cool air seeped through their clothes, and they shivered slightly, still not accustomed to it."
    "서늘한 공기가 옷 속을 파고들고, 당신은 아직 익숙하지 않은듯 작게 몸을 떱니다."

# game/OpeningScript.rpy:10
translate korean Opening_ifDead_47f019ed:

    # "You tried to shake the door to soothe your noisy hunger, but it didn't budge."
    "요란한 배를 달래기 위해 문을 흔들어 보지만 꿈쩍도 하지 않습니다."

# game/OpeningScript.rpy:11
translate korean Opening_ifDead_90addfa3:

    # "A cold sweat ran down your spine, and you fixed your gaze on the familiar staircase."
    "등골에 식은 땀이 한 줄 흐르고, 익숙한 계단에 시선을 고정합니다."

# game/OpeningScript.rpy:12
translate korean Opening_ifDead_6f68ddf1:

    # "You knew you had to move forward."
    "앞으로 나아가야만 합니다."

# game/OpeningScript.rpy:17
translate korean Opening_380ff76e:

    # "You opened the door of the tower and then cautiously stepped inside."
    "당신은 문을 열고 탑 안으로 들어갑니다."

# game/OpeningScript.rpy:18
translate korean Opening_01b682af:

    # "The warm sunshine you'd felt just a few moments before, the breeze that was pleasantly cool, if a little unseasonably so, contrasted with a chill, a faint musty odor."
    "발 걸음을 떼기 전 느꼈던 따스한 햇살, 조금 을씨년스럽지만 기분 좋게 시원했던 바람과는 대조되는 서늘함과 희미한 곰팡내가 느껴집니다."

# game/OpeningScript.rpy:19
translate korean Opening_73231c20:

    # "You heard the door close quietly between the creaking of gear and the faint echo of your footsteps."
    "장구류가 절그럭 거리는 소리, 작게 울리는 당신의 발소리 사이로 조용히 문이 닫히는 소리가 들립니다."

# game/OpeningScript.rpy:24
translate korean Opening_2c785407:

    # "You turned the handle, but the door wouldn't open. Now you have no choice but to move forward."
    "손잡이를 돌려 봤지만 열리지 않습니다.\n이젠 앞으로 나아가는 수밖에 없습니다."

